formThreeBId.notesToCertificate:
Note 1 : As per section 13 (1) of the RERA Act 2016, A promoter shall not accept more than 10 % of the value of consideration without first entering into written agreement with Allottees,  in few cases company has accepted more than 10 % of the consideration without entering into the written agreement (as per annexure A). 
As per Written representation received by management that despite company sending the model agreement for signatures and execution of Allottees, the Allottees never reverted with the signed agreements and continued to pay the money as per contractual milestones as per RERA. The company has also received the building use permission wide Ahmedabad Urban Development Authority (AUDA) CMP/5489/5/2018/247 dated 14th June 2018 and hence the final sale deed will now be executed with all such Allottees further project is registered as ongoing project under RERA

Note 2 : At the time of submitting form  3 we found that Estimated Cost is auto populated on the basis of Form -2, while filing the form 2 error is occur in putting the estimated cost 23,84,11,338/- rather than 17,48,49,944/-. On that basis change in percentage of completion         from 82.59% to 65.82%. same as amount deposited in designated bank account from 70% to 100%.
Due to technical reasons we could not able to update the data in Estimated Cost.
